WEBVTT

48:32.359 --> 48:34.150
His father was his world.

48:41.359 --> 48:42.984
It was dad's wish.

48:43.067 --> 48:44.859
My dad was everything to him.

48:50.400 --> 48:53.192
Each of the victims has achieved
greatness in their respective fields.

